1990;;Girlfriend from Hell;;American;;Daniel M. Peterson;;Dana Ashbrook;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Girlfriend_from_Hell;;Maggie (Liane Curtis) is a shy high school girl that isn't very good with men. This changes after she's possessed by Satan, who uses Maggie's body to seduce the souls out of various men. Satan is followed by an angelic Chaser (Dana Ashbrook), who is intent on capturing her once and for all.